Imo State – An angry Nigerian man has attacked the people of Mbaise in Imo state over outrageous marriage requirements. A local man has taken his grievances to Twitter ranting about the outrageous marriage requirements of the people of Mbaise in Imo state. The man identified as @AloyDSpeaker said he went to Mbaise with a relative who wanted to take a bride but the monetary and material requirements were just too many. He condemned the culture that fleeces prospective grooms and blamed this culture for the number of unmarried Mbaise women. Sharing the video, he wrote: “I Am so pained and right now my uncle said he is not ready to Marry again and I think the #mbaise people of IMO state should change their culture on marriage.” Watch the video below: Source